{"tid":1554874,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"環時：美國沒有對香港的高度自治，作出定義的權力","createTime":"2019-09-09T06:49:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-09T06:54:41.000Z","uid":149978,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"946df2b6ea5c99b651e47341c0b4ec11e8cdd8e4","tid":1554874,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T06:49:59.000Z","msg":"內地官方喉舌《環球時報》社評表示，香港的高度自治，美國沒有作出定義的權力。<br />\n<br />\n社評認為，美國如果通過干涉香港內政的「香港人權與民主法案」，是要將香港變成更有利於華盛頓向北京施壓的一張牌，而香港極少數人呼籲美國國會通過法案，他們已經完全喪失理性，寧願「攬炒」，試圖以對「一國兩制」搞「自殺式襲擊」的方式，劫持整個香港的命運。<br />\n<br />\n社評認為，中國有能力排除美國的各種干擾前進，香港的特殊關稅地位，不是美國對這座自由港的恩惠，它的本質是互利性質，香港的未來將取決於中國有多強大，而不取決於美國對香港持什麼態度。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1479564-20190909.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1479564-20190909.htm&d=uCl2s%2BJteilWOEmp%2BZl8kTDyw%2Fr9SRfH8QBX8OZV2FM%3D&h=1438da92\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1479564-20190909.htm&h=1a79d993\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1479564-20190909.htm</a>"},{"pid":"1131595663761da7ef6ebbf95e46306169aab5bd","tid":1554874,"uid":55955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T06:51:17.000Z","msg":"又口交<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f03a978fc6dde2ae896324588fb1d7e2e5e241e","tid":1554874,"uid":205462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T06:52:02.000Z","msg":"香港人唔同蝗，唔食草的"},{"pid":"91e922871b8031785c294db7501c7dd593cfb3c9","tid":1554874,"uid":317299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T06:52:45.000Z","msg":"【913 八月十五】 金鐘悼義士<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1554687\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1554687</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XySvw4Z.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%